ra Chet Holmgren in igralec Charlotte Hornets Brandon Miller.<\/p>\n<p>Za najbolj\u0161ega obrabnega igralca se potegujeta \u0161e francoski center Minnesote Timberwolves Rudy Gobert, dobil jo je \u017ee trikrat, in \u010dlan mo\u0161tva Miami Heat Bam Adebayo.<\/p>\n<p>Med tremi igralci, ki so najbolj napredovali, so Tyrese Maxey, Coby White in Alperen Sengun. Za trenerja leta pa so ostali v igri Mark Daigneault (Oklahoma City), Chris Finch (Minnesota) in Jamahl Mosley (Orlando).<\/p>\n<p>Vir: STA<br \/>\nFoto: Sportida.com<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Don\u010di\u0107 je bil najbolj\u0161i strelec rednega dela lige s povpre\u010djem 33,9 to\u010dke na tekmo, temu je dodal 9,2 skoka in 9,8 podaje. V sezoni 2018\/19 je bil izbran za najbolj\u0161ega novinca NBA, nato pa vsako sezono kon\u010dal med deseterico v glasovanju za MVP. V vseh naslednjih \u0161tirih sezonah je bil prav tako izbran na tekme &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.sport-tv.si\/doncic-med-tremi-finalisti-za-naziv-mvp-ja-lige-nba\/\">Continued<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":10409,"featured_media":216822,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[3],"tags":[1580,161,25],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.sport-tv.si\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/223856"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.sport-tv.si\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.sport-tv.si\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.sport-tv.si\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/10409"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.sport-tv.si\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=223856"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/www.sport-tv.si\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/223856\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":223859,"href":"https:\/\/www.sport-tv.si\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/223856\/revisions\/223859"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http